node.text: The ELIE SAAB Haute Couture Fall/Winter 2021/2022 collection is a colorful and whimsical dreamscape of rebirth and renewal, where each gown is generously sewn with seeds of hope, and where each bud is a promise of growth. The collection is a hopeful reminder of a new dawn and an eternal spring.

node.title: ELIE SAAB HAUTE COUTURE FALL/WINTER 2021-2022 - BUDS OF HOPE

node.text:
The ELIE SAAB Bridal Spring Summer 2022 embraces the unique feminine expressions of all brides with a radiant collection that embodies glamour, grace and allure @eliesaabbridal #ELIESAAB #ELIESAABBRIDAL 

Art Direction: @neimanazzi
Production and direction: @patricksawaya
Make up by @bassamfattouh
Hair by @wassimmorkos @paceeluce

ELIE SAAB Fall-Winter 2021/22 continues to celebrate the strong feminine mystique with a diverse ready-to-wear collection that exudes power in an ongoing conversation between soft and bold, flow and structure, delicate and wild #ELIESAAB

Production and direction: @patricksawaya
Music composed, produced and mixed by @ronyseikaly 
Makeup and Hair products @lorealparis 
Make up by @bassamfattouh 
Hair by @wassimmorkos @paceeluce 

#parisfashionweek #pfw #lorealparis #lorealpfw

node.text:
Taken in by the power of the ELIE SAAB Haute Couture Spring/Summer 2021 collection, they exhibit the strength, the daring and the courage to carry these larger-than-life pieces that are not only made of the stuff of dreams but also inspire to dream big, because dreaming keep us moving forward #ELIESAAB

Art Direction: @neimanazzi 
Production and direction: @patricksawaya 
Music: HVOB-Sync
HVOB-Bloom
HVOB-Panama (written and produced by Anna Mueller & Paul R. Wallner)

node.text:
Beirut's magical spirit is essential to Elie Saab's creation.He designs with Beirut, with its vibrant cultural imaginary and its rich artistic heritage. In this whimsical new collection Elie Saab shares with the world, he invokes the SACRED SOURCE, the throbbing life force that allows Beirut to triumph over and over again. He gives breath to a vestiary of beautiful divinities that embody the essences of his most beloved Beirut #ELIESAABHAUTECOUTURE
 
Fashion Film Directed by: @mounia.akl 
Produced by: @rajazgheib

node.text:
When the noises of our busy lives were silenced, only one sound emerged from within the deep void: the sound of the sacred source. While going back to the roots, we are paying homage to artistry and digging deep into the abundant beauty of nature #ELIESAABHAUTECOUTURE 

Video Directed by: @mounia.akl 
Produced by: @rajazgheib
